@{bg fill}                            @{fg shine}Preferences Mainmenu@{fg text}                            @{bg back}


          @{" Report Settings    " link "Report" 0}
          @{" Output Settings    " link "Output" 0}
          @{" Directory Settings " link "Dirs" 0}


          * Accept Settings
            Returns you to the main screen.

          * Preprogrammed Settings
            Resets all settings to the preprogrammed settings.

          * Load
            Loads the last saved settings.

          * Save
            Saves the settings to a config-file.



          @{" Back to Main               " link "Main" 0}

          @{" Proceed to Report Settings " link "Report" 0}

